flowRoot.flowPara: An analogue continuous tape, where one can record suggestions such as e.g. 2 + 2 = 5, which is automatically activated at certain times. The tape will automatically turn off after 5 minutes. With digital Equipment (computer / mobile phone / IoT) one can realize more complex systems. And there are possibly also several different cannels, (see cards t1, t7, t3, t12)

During the night: overwrite things (c05 card) or learning things while sleeping, eg. foreign languages, unfortunately you can also upload a complete (wrong) world view to the brain, or antagonizing world views or dogmas to split society into two groups that fight each other (see card m50, or eg. ma5 vs ma6)
